This article details the '''geographical distribution of speakers of the Italian language''', regardless of the legislative status within the countries where it is spoken. In addition to the [[Italian language|Italian]]-speaking area in [[Europe]], Italian-speaking [[minority language|minorities]] are present in many countries.
